{"tid":2358888,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Elon Musk都叫人用Signal。。。","createTime":"2021-01-08T12:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T04:35:44.000Z","uid":58335,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cf0e3236085f8c8424a0b869b01430a3cf3a6426","tid":2358888,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T12:42:00.000Z","msg":"Tesla股價創新高助Elon Musk登上全球首富。同為科技巨頭，Elon Musk一直以來也和Facebook集團合不來，Elon Musk最近就在Twitter上出post發言，叫大家「Use Signal」，言簡意賅，應該就是對WhatsApp近日的條款改動表示不滿。<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp日前更新使用條款，要求用家批准WhatsApp將用戶資料，包括電話號碼、聯絡人等分享予Facebook，而且要繼續用WhatsApp必須同意。外間估計。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nElon Musk開腔之後，帖文like數已過20萬，Signal下載數量急升，官方也要在Twitter發文，表示。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210108/3EGRSCTXIRFUBGZTFWGT6APFRQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210108%2F3EGRSCTXIRFUBGZTFWGT6APFRQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIYjsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=5fd0aa0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210108%2F3EGRSCTXIRFUBGZTFWGT6APFRQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post&h=d8a2d202\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210108/3EGRSCTXIRFUBGZTFWGT6APFRQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post</a>"},{"pid":"e940b8ce4b2deb4fc52c057e34473c4c49a53b54","tid":2358888,"uid":76804,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T12:58:26.000Z","msg":"希望佢可以build up另一個社交平台出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e697347c3c66d5c4b73a4a9976a65e6b1e3421d","tid":2358888,"uid":5303,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:04:45.000Z","msg":"條友成日讚中国<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1df43f5a37eb9d4987b5f5508547fc1ba844c5","tid":2358888,"uid":252541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:06:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://signalstickers.com/?s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsignalstickers.com%2F%3Fs&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIYjsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=9dbdabb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://signalstickers.com/?s</a>"},{"pid":"8eb6489ca4bf72daca57fb96703cf295af3b2549","tid":2358888,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:20:08.000Z","msg":"Elon Musk係藍&mdash;-》佢叫人用signal&mdash;-〉signal都係藍<br />\n<br />\n杯葛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a4d50450f22f5227343533f2b685c9830f16b8","tid":2358888,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:23:47.000Z","msg":"如果真的希望能保障私隱，令通訊內容免遭竊聽，在WhatsApp和Telegram以外，其實尚有更多通訊軟件可以使用，例如免費的開源軟件Signal。<br />\n電腦保安專家Moxie Marlinspike曾創立電腦保安公司Whisper Systems，創立了兩個加密通訊軟件Textsecure和Redphone。該公司其後被Twitter收購，Marlinspike亦因此加入Twitter的資訊安全團隊。<br />\n其後Whisper Systems把其軟件以開放源碼方式釋出，Marlinspike亦離開Twitter，成立「致力令私人通訊變得簡單」的非牟利組織Open Whisper Systems，負責開發和維護一些開源計劃，包括結合了Textsecure和Redphone的Signal。<br />\n<br />\n斯諾登推薦使用<br />\nSignal使用的通訊協定獲得專家認可，今年4月WhatsApp也是採用其協定，全面改為「端對端」加密。Open Whisper Systems又曾表示，其伺服器上不會儲存用戶的後設數據，以免洩露用戶資料。<br />\n而Signal的最佳代言人，應該是揭發美國國安局大規模監控民眾的斯諾登（Edward Snowden）。他曾多次讚揚Signal，在Open Whisper Systems的網站上更有斯諾登的圖片，以及其推薦語︰「使用Open Whisper Systems的任何產品。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/47867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F47867&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIYjsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=0ee5619a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/47867</a>"},{"pid":"70ff7b734751b6af886d98631c521895dddc10cd","tid":2358888,"uid":55597,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:33:59.000Z","msg":"香港人：其他人用 whatsapp 我冇得唔用 whatsapp"},{"pid":"2736198c06c2143157a44185d3cb42451282b34f","tid":2358888,"uid":4811,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"70ff7b734751b6af886d98631c521895dddc10cd","tid":2358888,"uid":55597,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:33:59.000Z","msg":"香港人：其他人用 whatsapp 我冇得唔用 whatsapp"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:49:23.000Z","msg":"其實只係裝個app，有時風向一轉無想像中咁難改變"},{"pid":"4af45c7b91ce28a17e72780da99faf880a0b12fa","tid":2358888,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2736198c06c2143157a44185d3cb42451282b34f","tid":2358888,"uid":4811,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"70ff7b734751b6af886d98631c521895dddc10cd","tid":2358888,"uid":55597,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:33:59.000Z","msg":"香港人：其他人用 whatsapp 我冇得唔用 whatsapp"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:49:23.000Z","msg":"其實只係裝個app，有時風向一轉無想像中咁難改變"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T15:01:35.000Z","msg":"linux 都唔難用"},{"pid":"7f77d58fee60024eeea65645dd26013304085f0c","tid":2358888,"uid":219,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T15:39:33.000Z","msg":"tg都唔推 首富好打有限"},{"pid":"bb71655accf8b0ead5cbb3d7cf11bce51bf58048","tid":2358888,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T04:2